defaultScience believes itself to be ‘gender neutral’ but this is an illusion that hides a whole range of gender bias effects. 
defaultUniversities 
defaultneed to 
defaultbe pro-active in encouraging 
defaultwomen to apply for research grants, by making sure that women’s teaching loads are not bigger than those of men
default, and that they are mentored appropriately.  When project teams are formed, they should be guid
