defaultIn 
defaultNorway, despite the acceptance of the quota mechanism for women, not one university has as yet achieved even 30% target of women professors.  Universities must examine their processes and practices for sources of gender bias and weed them out. T
defaulthe
default 
defaultUniversi
defaultty 
defaultof Tromso 
defaultimplemented a trial evaluation process designed to simulate the promotion process, thereby ensuring that women candidates can be confident that they are ready for promotion before applying. The Tromso board has also set the conditions that all
default advertised positions will have search committees specifically charged with finding women applicants, requiring that the applicant pool for any particular positi
defaulton has no fewer than 40% women, and has made available 
defaultfunds 
defaultfor department 
defaultchairs and deans 
defaultto
default 
defaultidentify specific support measures 
defaultsuch as 
defaultshort-term buy-outs from teaching duties, statistical support, research assistance, data processing support. 
